<div class="site-section border-top" style="text-align:center; justify-content:center;">
    <div class="container bushfire_loss_div">
        <div class="row bushfire_loss">
            <p>
                Each year bushfire is causing deaths and property damages in Victoria. The graph shows the losses from major bushfires. Individual preparations can minimize the numbers.
            </p>
            <iframe id="igraph" scrolling="no" style="border:none;" seamless="seamless" src="https://plotly.com/~yzha0400/5.embed" height="600" width="100%"></iframe>

        </div>
